# Binance Futures Testnet API Credentials
# 
# ⚠️  IMPORTANT: This file contains sensitive information
# ⚠️  NEVER commit this file to git (it's in .gitignore)
# ⚠️  KEEP YOUR API KEYS PRIVATE AND SECURE
#
# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Get your API keys from https://testnet.binancefuture.com
#    - API Management > Create New Key
#    - Select "Futures Trading" permission
#    - Copy the API Key and Secret
# 
# 2. Fill in the values below:
#
# 3. Source this file before running the bot:
#    source .env
#
# 4. Verify it's loaded:
#    echo $BINANCE_API_KEY
#

# Your Binance Testnet API Key
# Get from: https://testnet.binancefuture.com -> API Management
BINANCE_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Your Binance Testnet API Secret
# Get from: https://testnet.binancefuture.com -> API Management
BINANCE_API_SECRET=your_api_secret_here

# Optional: Base URL (pre-configured for testnet)
# BINANCE_BASE_URL=https://testnet.binancefuture.com

# Optional: Log directory
# LOG_DIR=logs
